4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week, with a maximum of 18 participants per class. Students will learn essential skills in Windows, Linux, and network/server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The curriculum also covers data loss prevention and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop